Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨在不可思議的國度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直做著長夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到短暫的夏日終結
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色的晚霞中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都是搖蕩的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的世界 不存在於夢中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年這間校舍就要被拆除了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.47,0:00:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業後充滿回憶的地方就要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捨不得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.23,0:00:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對後輩們來說可能不好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是充滿我們兩人回憶的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只存在於我們兩人的記憶裡 這也挺好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我什麼也沒看見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會對任何人說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.46,0:01:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕節禮物很快就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我比較笨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家…要去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:03:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？正月要去名古屋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，明天去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為媽媽的老家在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，請去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好，這樣做就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了媽媽，我要送美嶼回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母大人，打擾您這麼長時間，真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人的事今後拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到這裡就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真不巧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會這麼快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個怪人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你母親沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為，神名君就是神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我，那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候可以回來？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，4號一起去參拜神社吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ECO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,adove Tokyo together
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I say again safety
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,preengine AGM
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FS-306進入了戰鬥空域
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通線路無法恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？發生了什麼事？東京
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1+2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FS-306通信中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的機動性…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，無法追蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去全部機體都會被擊落的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了，甩不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了，那是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:06:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於現在已經中斷的與首都圈的通訊\N什麼時候能恢復的問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交通信息中心傳來的交通管制的通知…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙，太危險了，快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙、遙、遙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君、神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君、神名君、神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在這個世界見到這塊石版，真是沒有想到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon系統
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙人的時間調率的出現
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及根據哪一方進行世界的調率
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都與我之前所在的世界的是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說原本是相同的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙多元化的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這塊石板出現在MU和人的任何一方也不足為奇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，宇宙現在因為多元化使質量增大，就要崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快，這個世界也將消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須盡快搶回奏者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這一點，我們戰術部…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1+2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有合適的人選嗎？功刀君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報部有一個合適的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是女性，能力方面沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和奏者認識
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，這次的Overlord作戰就交給你的作戰部了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:07:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然趕不上這次的作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是無論如何我會使由您提供的Vermilion趕上反攻作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Down Fall作戰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來沒想過要採取那種行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo Jupiter嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，障壁…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們得到了準備的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它內部與外部有6倍的時間變換
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事態是向對我們有利的方向發展的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位奏者，並非純血…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說和六道說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位奏者流淌著MU的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一樣，MU的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久時刻來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界被調率
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界將再次被純潔的音色所充滿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總裁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的房間開放的時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到這個時間了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴貝姆先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去睡美人那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了？睡美人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼異狀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有甦醒的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，奏者這種東西不管何時看到都很美麗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個印記
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，已經成長到這個地步了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快了，就快可以見面了，我的久遠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天又做了那個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃昏的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們初次約會的那天一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡我發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經不在了的我的女友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼遙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我追趕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻追不上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追啊、追
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我認為已經追上的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那以來已經過了3年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上除東京以外其它地方都滅亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下2300萬人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:11:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此，卻好像什麼事也沒有發生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的日常生活繼續著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在忘記過去的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與之相對，夢漸漸地鮮明瞭起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這樣也不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為我擁有她活著的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…美嶼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在一定在什麼地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守！嘿，守！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:11:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈！朝比奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名…君…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥飼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥飼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，你沒事吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥飼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照看好守！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪兒啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就去找人來幫忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君！神名君！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！一個人都沒有嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的平民！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真礙事，閃開！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著！你還活著吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美嶼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼、美嶼、美嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神名綾人君吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您母親找你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有時間做解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你和我們一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我解釋…清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太頑固了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見嘍！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以算是正義的使者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救了你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你至少能說聲謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在危險之中救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「為什麼血的顏色是藍的？」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你跟我來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色血的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走，求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你求我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是那種會傻乎乎地跟著陌生人走的小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我必須去救我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣，你不覺得太過分了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，不知道的話也許會更幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會被那種比我們老兩代的戰鬥機擊落啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是delta-1號，各機請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標已經被愛麗絲保護
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知各機，任務進入第2階段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha-1明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是Alpha-1，各機請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匯合，進入第2階段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要覺醒的話還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在Terra手裡12小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:18:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們阻止這種上升的事態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共鳴程度已經開始上升了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，好像是麻醉藥效果太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被綁架了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想知道這個世界的一切？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在地球上有多少人，你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然說這個幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2300萬人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是60億人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，停車！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我下車！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你不感興趣，我也要讓你看到一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好，接下來我們就要突破障壁到外面去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呀？「障壁」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是隱藏真相的「障壁」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從RahXephon傳來的波動？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人還沒有做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，無法阻止共鳴程度的上升
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，聽指揮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡、可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要Xephon開始活動，就立即啟動Dolem
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接去Rah的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了，綾人君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…在召喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人君，振作點！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生共鳴了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻彌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.87,0:22:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:22:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺醒了吧，綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的東西太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.23,0:23:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？你在說什麼，媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等待，你的血在你的體內覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.33,0:23:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dolem有量子凝聚反應
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FD相位變換在增大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.33,0:23:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的變換係數…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.75,0:23:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它覺醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.17,0:23:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？聽不清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.59,0:23:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dolem被Xephon…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.51,0:23:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.61,0:23:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:23:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回來，綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.37,0:23:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君，不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.93,0:24:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.59,0:25:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不聽我的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.26,0:25:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.86,0:25:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.87,0:25:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我、我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.38,0:25:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Xephon的量子凝聚持續增大至測量極限值
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.13,0:25:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,級別：12+
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.72,0:25:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是綾人大人的力量嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.26,0:26:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.26,0:26:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量子凝聚呈偶極子型收縮
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.84,0:26:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在與邊界融合
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.93,0:26:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通道形成了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.02,0:26:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Xephon好像已經跳躍出了障壁
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.44,0:26:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳躍出障壁？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.77,0:26:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.69,0:26:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Xephon和奏者在外面！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.44,0:26:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.53,0:26:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧，綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.87,0:26:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你一定會回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.79,0:26:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無法使那種力量增長
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.49,0:27:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兒也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.33,0:27:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有能用的通訊設備
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.67,0:27:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我該怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.33,0:27:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.92,0:27:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.59,0:27:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.26,0:27:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.26,0:27:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像牆一樣的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.84,0:27:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.93,0:27:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，你是第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.43,0:27:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是Tokyo Jupiter
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.68,0:27:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很像木星吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.52,0:27:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo…Jupiter…？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.44,0:27:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.27,0:27:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之前，對你來說就是整個世界的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.27,0:27:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.44,0:27:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.54,0:28:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.05,0:28:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.22,0:28:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也有責任啊，站在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.07,0:28:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三浦半島？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.73,0:28:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的世界不是在很久以前就被毀滅了嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.57,0:28:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是他們灌輸給你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.16,0:28:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而這個地方的確還存在著
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.83,0:28:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以至信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.16,0:28:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.16,0:28:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不輕易相信是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.33,0:29:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許這是我為了欺騙你而編造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.84,0:29:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.34,0:29:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我想騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.17,0:29:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會告訴你這些事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.43,0:29:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，你和我都快感冒了倒是事實！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.52,0:29:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.02,0:29:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽就要下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.52,0:29:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回RahXephon那裡，再找個休息的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.36,0:29:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.86,0:29:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.11,0:29:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個長著翅膀的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.53,0:29:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你操縱了它呀
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.37,0:29:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.62,0:29:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.12,0:29:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天下午公佈了參加喀布爾奧運會的\N日本滑板隊的成員名單
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.46,0:29:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女隊在前屆2024年平壤奧運會上…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.22,0:29:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2024年？！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.39,0:29:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.64,0:29:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才他說了2024年吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.89,0:29:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.97,0:29:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在不是…2015年嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.56,0:30:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是1998年出生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.06,0:30:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你17歲，對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.73,0:30:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，有點混亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.99,0:30:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天應該是11月10日吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.99,0:30:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11月？！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.58,0:30:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2027年
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.66,0:30:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你來自未來？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.67,0:30:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.92,0:30:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實是殘酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.09,0:30:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想聽我解釋嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.27,0:30:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使聽了也未必能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.44,0:30:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意我說的話吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.69,0:30:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是認為這可能是某種陰謀？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.95,0:30:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不像愛戀那麼甜蜜，也不像惡魔那樣漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.03,0:30:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這只是咖啡，沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.45,0:31:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺自己有點像浦島太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.37,0:31:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於那個玉匣來說RahXephon可太大了點
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.21,0:31:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在遇到你之前，我看到了我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.05,0:31:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是叫Tokyo Jupiter吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.56,0:31:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那個東西出現時起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.06,0:31:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就應該不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.31,0:31:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是夢吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.48,0:31:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.32,0:31:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.32,0:31:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.65,0:31:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了很多人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.74,0:31:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個東西出現
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.32,0:31:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.74,0:31:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，同樣很多人活了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.25,0:31:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.67,0:31:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.75,0:31:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.92,0:31:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.92,0:31:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…在這個世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.19,0:32:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人君？！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.16,0:33:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個的對面是你們的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.16,0:33:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這裡距離障壁大約有10公里
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.91,0:33:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據推測地下的部分應該也是半球狀
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.58,0:33:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有這個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.42,0:33:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前，雖然對你來說是3年前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.59,0:33:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從異次元來的侵略者MU
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.34,0:33:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像為了保護什麼製造了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.35,0:33:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般的看法是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.68,0:33:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是RahXephon？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.68,0:33:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迄今為止這個世界好像什麼事也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.36,0:33:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過最近世界各地觀測到了MU出現的徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.95,0:33:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看到那個和你做戰的人形就能明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.53,0:33:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥力的差距是壓倒性的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.37,0:33:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要是再度進攻的話，人類很難與之對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.29,0:33:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望能得到你的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.96,0:33:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你用你的RahXephon…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.97,0:33:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.22,0:34:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須借助你的力量，否則人類會滅亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.14,0:34:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我無法強制你那樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.64,0:34:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣就是要你對故鄉拔刀相向
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.57,0:34:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已經拔刀了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.32,0:34:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.32,0:34:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事不管如何道歉都不可能得到原諒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.26,0:34:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.03,0:35:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了，讓我們等這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.37,0:35:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉麗亞？立特巴克
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.87,0:35:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.04,0:35:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Terra下屬的特別任務航空母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.79,0:35:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Terra？Terra是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.54,0:35:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對MU戰略研究機關
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.71,0:35:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我工作的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.72,0:35:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Terra情報部第二情報課特別任務大尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.05,0:35:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫東…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.56,0:35:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫東遙
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.06,0:35:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.64,0:35:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙…小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.65,0:35:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來，我們的情報部真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.99,0:35:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的Overlord作戰的目的本來是捕獲奏者
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.24,0:35:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不得了的附贈品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.58,0:35:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的全部力量建造的基地和我們Terra的戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.66,0:35:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上那個RahXephon的話
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.25,0:35:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個反攻作戰就不再是夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.92,0:36:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹博士
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.17,0:36:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它現在到了我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.76,0:36:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣，不過來看看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.02,0:36:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.02,0:36:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.11,0:36:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.95,0:36:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的，不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.12,0:36:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.87,0:36:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他覺醒了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.04,0:36:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你、你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.63,0:36:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.38,0:36:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就會救你出去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.47,0:36:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是上岸而已
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.14,0:36:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼非要做血液檢察
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.48,0:36:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只不過是種形式
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.65,0:36:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.16,0:37:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.32,0:37:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是MU Phase
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.33,0:37:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過血還是紅的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.16,0:37:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.25,0:37:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.42,0:37:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總有一天會覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.92,0:37:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那時刻來到之前\N我們必須能利用什麼就利用什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.34,0:37:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.27,0:37:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.02,0:37:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是MU族專用監禁室吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.52,0:37:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要強行打開的話，室內的人就會被炸死
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.44,0:37:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指標活體分子的分析結果出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.78,0:37:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的核甘酸序列都吻合，是MU-Phase反應
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.62,0:37:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他什麼都不知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.79,0:37:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求您，解除他的監禁！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.62,0:38:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該會合作的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.54,0:38:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之，他和我們一樣是流著紅色血液的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.38,0:38:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.72,0:38:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總有一天會變藍
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.64,0:38:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是奏者，不，神名綾人的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.97,0:38:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血變藍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.73,0:38:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去記憶被消除，替換上MU的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.73,0:38:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為MU族的奏者，會對世界進行調率
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.82,0:38:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之，那是對我們的世界的否定
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.66,0:38:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味著人類的滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.66,0:38:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了阻止它的發生而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.33,0:38:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色血液的階段也是為了世界的調率（做準備）
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.92,0:38:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當無法阻止時
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.09,0:38:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.17,0:38:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.26,0:38:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會殺死神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.84,0:38:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我被賦予的真正使命
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.18,0:38:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.27,0:39:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，原本沒有這種打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.19,0:39:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.94,0:39:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是因為我能操縱RahXephon嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.69,0:39:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關係吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.61,0:39:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我母親的血是藍色的這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.45,0:39:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好，你能看看這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.88,0:39:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Terra，不，由聯合國認定的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.55,0:39:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為這次戰爭的最重要的證人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.63,0:39:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MU的最高指揮者-神名麻彌
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.14,0:39:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你母親
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.06,0:39:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.14,0:39:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初，MU好像打算與人類共存
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.65,0:39:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，他們最初出現時所發的信件
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.07,0:39:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被聯合國秘密地保管著
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.07,0:39:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果事態的發展卻與之相反
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.49,0:40:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然理由不明，但他們發動了戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.91,0:40:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅一天之內，世界上就死了幾萬人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.59,0:40:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合國做了全面戰爭的心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.17,0:40:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那場戰爭卻沒有實行
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.59,0:40:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.18,0:40:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為出現了Tokyo Jupiter
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.18,0:40:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們躲在了那個屏障之後
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.68,0:40:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是在等待著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.19,0:40:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這並不意味著戰爭消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.27,0:40:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今還在發動零散地進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.03,0:40:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他們而言，可能只是管管閒事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.53,0:40:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但危害很大
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.37,0:40:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，綁架我，作為人質啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.12,0:40:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說，你的血是紅的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.79,0:40:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們的血的顏色不是一樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.29,0:40:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是媽媽的血…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.05,0:40:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.13,0:40:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有關係啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.05,0:40:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的母親沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.89,0:40:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.97,0:41:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.98,0:41:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我想起了奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.06,0:41:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.73,0:41:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去有人對我說過同樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.98,0:41:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我至今還喜歡的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.83,0:41:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.74,0:41:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.99,0:41:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你見一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.91,0:41:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就會安心
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.83,0:41:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.34,0:41:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說久遠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.42,0:41:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不能讓你見久遠
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.09,0:41:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.59,0:41:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.84,0:41:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個…如月博士
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.43,0:41:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我樹就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.77,0:41:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.02,0:41:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…樹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.35,0:41:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠是…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.94,0:41:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由Terra科學調查部監管的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.44,0:41:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最重要睡美人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.36,0:41:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡美人？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.36,0:42:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直在這個神殿--奈利亞神殿深處睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.95,0:42:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不時會醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.04,0:42:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我們各種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.04,0:42:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像預知夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.46,0:42:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，不，也許可能是世界的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.29,0:42:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠的身體雖然在這邊，但她的靈魂卻在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.97,0:42:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.38,0:42:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MU的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.14,0:42:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她作為擁有藍色血液的神聖MU族
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.14,0:42:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是RahXephon的原形奏者
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.98,0:42:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠她一直在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.06,0:42:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒了的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.15,0:42:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想真正地拯救世界，就必須使她醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.99,0:42:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在並不是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.66,0:42:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以當那時刻來臨時，我會告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.91,0:42:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.41,0:42:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要到政府機關去辦一下手續
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.42,0:42:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父、惠接下來就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.85,0:43:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.68,0:43:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家特意買來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.85,0:43:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（這裡）和你的城市、你家大不一樣吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.36,0:43:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時可能會不習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.94,0:43:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，就當成去親戚家玩
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.61,0:43:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.62,0:43:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不太瞭解那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.37,0:43:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒去過親戚家玩
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.22,0:43:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，惠
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.72,0:43:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離吃晚飯還有一段時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.72,0:43:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶綾人君到附近看看
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.14,0:43:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.14,0:43:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？伯父我平時是怎麼對你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.48,0:43:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.23,0:43:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我無所謂…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.32,0:44:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京是個什麼樣的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.15,0:44:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.16,0:44:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的城市而已
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.74,0:44:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以為那裡會有什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.83,0:44:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.99,0:44:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為以前啊，我姐姐說過一定要回到東京
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.75,0:44:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐？是遙小姐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.84,0:44:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，因為她是在東京出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.92,0:44:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.09,0:44:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.26,0:44:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.68,0:44:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為聽說你是東京人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.43,0:44:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你會是個可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.18,0:44:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.04,0:44:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊？小球堵著喝不到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.96,0:44:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.63,0:44:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.54,0:45:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真笨，要把小球移到凹坑裡去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.89,0:45:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼爽！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.65,0:45:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…六道先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.23,0:45:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我伯父就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.99,0:45:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.24,0:45:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.07,0:45:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父平時常對惠說的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.08,0:45:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.25,0:45:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逃避自己討厭的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.58,0:45:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼都從正面去接受
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.59,0:45:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她還年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.17,0:45:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.43,0:45:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個掛在門口
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.02,0:46:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各單位的最終確認
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.03,0:46:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民的避難和迎擊部隊隊形散開已經完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.36,0:46:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變的願意駕駛了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.12,0:46:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.28,0:46:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他喜歡這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.12,0:46:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像還沒有明白啊，紫東大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.46,0:46:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼願意駕駛了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.55,0:46:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.97,0:46:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該沒有去戰鬥的理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.06,0:46:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個對我來說很重要的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.48,0:46:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在東京？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.65,0:46:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.65,0:46:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該在什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.32,0:46:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去曾經交往過的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.74,0:46:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想再見她一次
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.16,0:46:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想保護這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.33,0:46:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微不足道的理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.25,0:47:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.79,0:47:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去，MU不會什麼都不做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.54,0:47:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.63,0:47:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會來把他帶回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.38,0:47:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這邊也是沒有預料到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.13,0:47:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會把RahXephon一起帶出來
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.55,0:47:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.64,0:47:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.89,0:48:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的真正王牌財團好像還沒有注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.56,0:48:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向世界調率的王牌，是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.65,0:48:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕麻彌也沒有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.15,0:48:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正需要的東西是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.74,0:48:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是犯罪吧…我們
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.66,0:48:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用紫東大尉的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.08,0:48:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管以什麼形式
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.75,0:48:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要她們能幸福就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.17,0:48:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不多奢求什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.26,0:48:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王牌她是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.18,0:48:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她知道了我們真正需要的\N並非是RahXephon的話
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.52,0:48:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們能夠寬恕我們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.94,0:48:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我們有我們的承擔責任的方式」
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.02,0:48:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是老師您說過的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.11,0:48:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有老師您的名譽我是不會讓它受損的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.62,0:49:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，仁
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.13,0:49:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨在不可思議的國度
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.96,0:49:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直做著長夢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.05,0:49:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到短暫的夏日終結
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.14,0:49:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色的晚霞中
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.06,0:49:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都是搖蕩的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.15,0:49:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的世界不是夢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.42,0:49:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.26,0:49:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.93,0:50:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是第幾回了？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.53,0:50:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.78,0:50:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那天一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.62,0:50:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真有毅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.37,0:50:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這樣努力呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.37,0:50:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為我是為了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.79,0:50:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了工作而鍛煉體力嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.46,0:50:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼衣服啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.05,0:50:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.64,0:50:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒有冬裝
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.89,0:50:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.73,0:50:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個，收下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.98,0:50:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.48,0:50:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，這是哪兒來的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.74,0:51:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師產生諧波(harmonies
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.74,0:51:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1產生強烈的輻射)
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.32,0:51:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1+2
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.49,0:51:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha小隊在幹什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.83,0:51:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為D-1的產生的電磁屏蔽，半徑50km內無法接近
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.84,0:51:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1的輻射與機師產生干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.26,0:51:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦波急劇混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.84,0:51:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師的心率快速下降！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.68,0:51:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去，綾人會…！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.43,0:51:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EMP脈衝調製模式與RahXephon的聲紋同步
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.02,0:51:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.02,0:51:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1形態變化，RahXephon被捕獲
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.03,0:51:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…通向未知區域的通道正在形成！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.04,0:51:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.62,0:51:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.04,0:51:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！綾人！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.89,0:52:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1進入邊界面
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.39,0:52:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與RahXephon的通訊中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.65,0:52:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.49,0:52:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你回來，綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.49,0:52:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.09,0:52:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽，停車！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.85,0:52:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像變了，神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.35,0:52:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.35,0:52:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有那麼大的變化吧，只是一星期而已
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.69,0:52:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一星期？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.03,0:53:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面…卻是一個月
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.53,0:53:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師也什麼都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.61,0:53:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家對神名君的失蹤完全不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.87,0:53:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得…總覺得有什麼不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.29,0:53:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直…我想再見神名君一次，當面問你…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.54,0:53:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不知道該問你些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.96,0:53:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.13,0:53:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對那些怪事情考慮得過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.72,0:53:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人只是因為家裡有重要的事，外出旅行而已
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.97,0:53:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.23,0:53:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，關於那場戰爭學校裡有什麼傳聞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.48,0:53:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.57,0:53:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戰爭，有入侵者…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.82,0:53:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.57,0:53:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼，別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.49,0:53:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭…？你看…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.08,0:53:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，我一定是忘記了某些重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.24,0:53:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，對…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.83,0:53:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得發生過什麼嚴重的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.67,0:53:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩子，夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.86,0:54:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.19,0:54:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的媽媽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.43,0:55:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.85,0:55:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人？你！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.35,0:55:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.44,0:55:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩，沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.62,0:55:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.57,0:56:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了，Falsetto
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.07,0:56:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微平靜一些了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.99,0:56:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.58,0:56:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人類稱為MU族的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.33,0:56:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕大部分的都沒能到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.00,0:56:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上救生船的只是很少的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.00,0:56:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到現在，他們還是那種不與Dolem同步
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.84,0:57:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法生存下去的藍色血液的人
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.59,0:57:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，MU族也是人
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.18,0:57:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.68,0:57:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.18,0:57:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是MU族嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.77,0:57:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.35,0:57:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你說的在我小的時候就去世父親也是的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.69,0:57:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經記不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.03,0:57:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是我們的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.95,0:57:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我愛你，只有這一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.37,0:57:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1+2
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.54,0:57:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不愛父親嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.71,0:57:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為什麼要生我？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.13,0:57:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.38,0:57:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥飼，你到底是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.14,0:57:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.06,0:57:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在欺騙我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.48,0:57:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那樣，就輕鬆多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.56,0:57:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩子，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.07,0:57:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.82,0:58:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等…不要！不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.09,0:58:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.68,0:58:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…媽媽你生我是為了與人類作戰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.27,0:58:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本必須由我去駕駛RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.78,0:58:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是我的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.28,0:58:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在記憶變回MU族的記憶的是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.78,0:58:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腹中已經有了你
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.70,0:58:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼理由
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.04,0:58:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我想看看你
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.96,0:58:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.05,0:59:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我卻撫養、培育了你
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.80,0:59:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法避免，加在我身上的命運交給了你
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.39,0:59:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我這雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.98,0:59:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒我也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.56,0:59:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我們無法逃避命運
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.90,0:59:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後的事，請自己決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.48,0:59:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼走，選擇什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.84,0:59:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.85,0:59:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allegretto到底在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.44,1:00:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.86,1:00:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.70,1:00:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.20,1:00:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.29,1:00:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.54,1:00:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.96,1:00:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看…我的血
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.80,1:00:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紅色的吧？是不是？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.97,1:00:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.64,1:00:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，紅色的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.73,1:00:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.23,1:00:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.40,1:00:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈，我已經不能再留在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.40,1:00:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能待在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.40,1:00:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話，我也是一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.74,1:00:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.07,1:00:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈，我…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.24,1:00:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.16,1:00:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.50,1:01:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.34,1:01:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君…我知道神名君無法忘記美嶼的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.17,1:01:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，即便如此也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.84,1:01:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.37,1:01:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.73,1:02:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Olin！
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.24,1:02:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.08,1:02:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是支付日薪的那種
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.58,1:02:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君，你是覺得應該負起責任才做的？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.75,1:02:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的，朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.84,1:02:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道不能總是這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.42,1:02:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.68,1:02:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.26,1:02:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要時間
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.60,1:02:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考的時間
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.18,1:02:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道現在該做什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.77,1:02:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果有時間的話我想我會想出來的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.85,1:02:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君，我…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.44,1:02:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.78,1:02:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天，我會用RahXephon把守和你的父母從東京帶出來的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.28,1:02:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.20,1:03:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在很幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.70,1:03:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是神名君能到我身邊，我已經很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.13,1:03:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我感覺的到
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.80,1:03:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時間無法長久
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.38,1:03:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.47,1:03:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多麼努力去回憶
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.47,1:03:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想不起爸爸和媽媽的事情來
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.39,1:03:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.23,1:03:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕呀
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.40,1:03:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，神名君
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.57,1:03:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.49,1:03:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.58,1:03:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.08,1:03:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君你決定吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.00,1:03:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸豬排怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.59,1:03:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太想吃肉
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.59,1:03:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就吃些清淡的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.76,1:03:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麵條有點…到底吃什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.85,1:04:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈？果然身體不舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.69,1:04:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君，那個，我…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.03,1:04:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情想和你說
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.94,1:04:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀？突然鄭重起來了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.78,1:04:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…最近…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.05,1:04:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…想吃Vongole
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.05,1:04:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.57,1:04:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.15,1:04:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dolem
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.65,1:04:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dolem？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.66,1:04:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的敵人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.16,1:05:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.07,1:05:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.66,1:05:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon！
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.67,1:05:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.09,1:05:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.84,1:05:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以為自己在東京沒有失去任何東西
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.77,1:05:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.10,1:05:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.60,1:05:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有必須去保護的人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.27,1:05:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護你，我想保護你
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.69,1:05:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.20,1:05:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.78,1:05:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打敗它
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.20,1:05:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君，我有話必須要對你說！
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.87,1:05:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心，我一定會回來
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.79,1:05:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請在這裡等我
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.12,1:05:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…想和神名君你說更多的話！
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.38,1:05:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道更多關於神名君你的事情！
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.46,1:05:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想你更多地瞭解我的事情！
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.47,1:06:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…綾人君！
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.80,1:06:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會永遠等你，永遠！永遠！永遠等你
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.39,1:06:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡等你綾人！
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.15,1:06:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人、綾人、綾人、綾人、綾人
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.34,1:06:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴他…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.09,1:06:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴他…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.84,1:06:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴他…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.18,1:06:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴綾人君…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.04,1:07:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了！我決定了！
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.12,1:07:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護她我…我…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.14,1:07:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護她，我要保護她
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.81,1:07:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.15,1:07:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴他…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.90,1:07:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說不行…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.65,1:07:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴綾人君…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.58,1:07:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…綾人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.87,1:08:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1200回收部隊到達現場
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.63,1:08:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標的保護以及回收成功
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.88,1:08:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赴旅館的特務班
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.13,1:08:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了與目標同行的D-1同步者
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.05,1:08:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現時已經死亡
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.47,1:08:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據推測很可能是當場喪生
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.73,1:09:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君…奏者看到了死者的死狀嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.99,1:09:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他好像在她的屍體旁號哭
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.83,1:09:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於屍體，他與特務班方面發生了糾紛
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.00,1:09:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在糾紛中有血從奏者的口中流出
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.25,1:09:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那血
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.17,1:09:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那血？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.84,1:09:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那血好像變藍了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.43,1:09:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.60,1:09:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體什麼問題也沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.35,1:09:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀司令說要解除了你的監控狀態
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.36,1:09:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.19,1:09:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好別和血變藍的人扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.36,1:09:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.70,1:09:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這種事情沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.87,1:09:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.87,1:09:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有活著的價值
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.45,1:09:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.95,1:09:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.46,1:09:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.12,1:10:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你說有什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.13,1:10:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.05,1:10:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是劊子手啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.88,1:10:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈她說她會等我
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.30,1:10:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我有無法忘記的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.56,1:10:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此她還在等
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.64,1:10:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能保護朝比奈的只有我
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.48,1:10:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下我了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.65,1:10:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.65,1:10:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才去戰鬥啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.65,1:10:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果…結果…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.24,1:10:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.74,1:10:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不能待在這邊的世界了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.49,1:10:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不想去駕駛了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.75,1:10:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon之類的東西
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.00,1:10:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想去駕駛了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.59,1:10:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，不再駕駛也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.09,1:10:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要綾人君能平安回來
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.26,1:10:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，只要能活著
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.68,1:11:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.27,1:11:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…請不要說這種話
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.69,1:11:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要哭
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.69,1:11:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我害怕！
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.45,1:11:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在了這種事，只要一想到就…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.06,1:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.73,1:11:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後悔了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.06,1:11:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到不是
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.56,1:11:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是被監視了嗎？這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.40,1:11:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.23,1:11:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.99,1:11:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直、一直…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.16,1:11:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.58,1:12:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我再這個樣子一會
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.66,1:12:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪人
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.75,1:12:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很認真啊，她
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.67,1:12:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的吧，因為在看情報部的極密資料嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.34,1:12:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.84,1:12:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她喜歡工作啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.35,1:12:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有男朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.60,1:12:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.43,1:12:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不，你看遙小姐工作能力強而且是個美人
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.19,1:12:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有些冒冒失失地…
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.27,1:12:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.03,1:12:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.53,1:12:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久之前好像有過
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.95,1:12:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.28,1:12:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是我出生之前的事呀
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.53,1:12:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的換姓之前的事
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.70,1:12:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我們的父親不一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.04,1:12:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.29,1:12:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫東是繼父的姓啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.29,1:12:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是個很美的姓啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.38,1:12:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的島嶼
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.30,1:13:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓，寫出來是「美麗的島嶼」
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.39,1:13:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念起來是「美嶼」
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.47,1:13:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我雖然是紫東惠
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.73,1:13:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實姐姐叫美嶼遙
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.65,1:13:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.74,1:13:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.17,1:13:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.83,1:13:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你在裡面
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.59,1:13:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.25,1:13:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地泡吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.75,1:13:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過會兒再來
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.09,1:13:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓…
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.18,1:13:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓…你換過姓吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.44,1:13:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.77,1:13:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.20,1:14:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位，由我們推進的對MU反攻作戰\N終於就要迎來它的結局了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.54,1:14:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次東京進攻作戰
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.12,1:14:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Overlord作戰後這種膠著狀態很快就要結束了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.88,1:14:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由這次的Down Fall作戰
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.05,1:14:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次，會使用不久前開發出來的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.63,1:14:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由聯合的MTL機構提供的概率諧振波展開系統
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.97,1:14:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消滅Tokyo Jupiter的絕對障壁
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.23,1:14:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動代號：J-Buster
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.48,1:14:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經秘密建造完成
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.98,1:14:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有以新型機動兵器VERMILION為中心\N兩個大隊向東京進攻
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.57,1:14:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消滅敵人的機動兵器和抵抗力量
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.58,1:14:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是Terra，不，是投入了人類全力的作戰
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.25,1:14:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我們戰術部指揮
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.09,1:14:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.59,1:14:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法陪伴您，對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.92,1:15:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句話應該我說
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.59,1:15:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為必須讓你跟著戰術部
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.26,1:15:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.93,1:15:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為實際行動的是我們的作戰部
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.19,1:15:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀先生請放心，推進您的計劃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.10,1:15:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.44,1:15:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你們是可靠的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.94,1:15:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，這個角色功刀先生最合適
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.86,1:15:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟隨老師的意志
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.37,1:15:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替被驅逐的老師，進行行動的我們
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.70,1:15:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是六道老師的大弟子的功刀先生您就不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.96,1:15:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做為六道學校的弟子中的一員
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.38,1:15:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是我的請求
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.30,1:15:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.97,1:15:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.80,1:15:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.47,1:15:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您女兒的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.48,1:15:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了不少力氣吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.98,1:15:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是從所有與財團有關的人士那裡收集來的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.07,1:16:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生過什麼事情？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.49,1:16:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會下場消暑的雨嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.07,1:16:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父！
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.49,1:16:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有她愛的男人
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.24,1:16:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人知道她擁有成為RahXephon奏者的資格
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.67,1:16:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此也愛她
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.75,1:16:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以當麻彌的腹中接受到新生命的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.26,1:16:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然兩人都很年輕
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.09,1:16:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是祝福了他們
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.60,1:16:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個時候，她
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.27,1:16:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻彌的血已經變藍了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.27,1:16:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛酸啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.94,1:16:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的失去記憶
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.86,1:16:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是連所愛的男人也忘記啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.53,1:16:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此，她還是說
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.20,1:16:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.45,1:16:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使記憶消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.29,1:16:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.95,1:16:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相愛的事實是不會消失的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.87,1:16:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼伯母大人她…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.29,1:17:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被財團發現了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.05,1:17:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人的孩子的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.47,1:17:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們並不想人類與奏者交往
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.05,1:17:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是所謂的「沒有結果」
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.80,1:17:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放他們逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.14,1:17:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說女兒要比RahXephon之類的東西更重要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.98,1:17:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天後
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.15,1:17:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了那個叫神名的男孩的屍體
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.65,1:17:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然財團拚命尋找麻彌的行蹤
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.66,1:17:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像終究未能找到
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.16,1:17:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到Tokyo Jupiter出現的那天
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.58,1:17:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她哭了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.50,1:17:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使流著淚，她也要自己選擇自己的路
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.75,1:17:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是明白的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.09,1:17:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有血緣關係
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.26,1:17:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她是我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.10,1:17:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人他會選擇什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.60,1:17:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次他坐上RahXephon…
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.27,1:18:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓神名君去坐的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.27,1:18:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.94,1:18:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論用什麼手段
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.36,1:18:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，不過…
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.53,1:18:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要你們幸福就夠了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.46,1:18:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.88,1:18:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.14,1:18:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你記起來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.56,1:18:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.98,1:18:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士的JB-3，啟動準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.90,1:18:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JB-1，預定配置完成
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.65,1:18:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本莊的JB-4，啟動準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.99,1:18:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大島的JB-2，啟動沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.74,1:19:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠間的JB-5，啟動準備完成
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.08,1:19:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支柱衛星的編隊怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.25,1:19:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問題，配置完成
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.50,1:19:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全系統配置完成
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.17,1:19:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動裝置沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.68,1:19:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就只是等待最高負責人下達命令了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.68,1:19:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Down Fall作戰啟動
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.43,1:19:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Operation Down Fall 啟動\NOperation Down Fall 啟動
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.27,1:19:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒計時15秒
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.54,1:19:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.48,1:19:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.41,1:19:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.29,1:19:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.55,1:19:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.70,1:19:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,zero
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.70,1:19:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,概率諧振波，展開！
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.05,1:19:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是…久遠小姐？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.97,1:19:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.06,1:20:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…王子終於覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.98,1:20:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.56,1:20:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.65,1:20:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.48,1:20:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次輪到你讓她甦醒了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.40,1:20:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她甦醒…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.90,1:20:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.49,1:20:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要吻她就可以了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.32,1:20:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是王子的使命吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.33,1:20:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話樹先生來做不就行了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.08,1:20:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我可以，我早就做了！
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.00,1:20:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了，快做！
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.75,1:20:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，做呀！
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.25,1:20:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等，樹先生
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.59,1:20:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1+2
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.00,1:20:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做呀！
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.09,1:20:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做呀！
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.27,1:20:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於見到了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.93,1:20:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在等著
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.19,1:20:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在毀滅之音充滿之前
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.69,1:20:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能與你們相遇真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.69,1:20:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人也沒有問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.45,1:20:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，樹
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.36,1:20:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護我的人
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.95,1:21:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛的人
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.29,1:21:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.87,1:21:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也愛你
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.23,1:21:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo Jupiter 絕對障壁
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.48,1:21:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認消除
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.73,1:21:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她過去曾經要對世界進行調率
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.99,1:21:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在MU的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.74,1:21:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻失敗了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.99,1:21:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以被炸飛到了這個世界
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.83,1:21:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的母親、巴貝姆一起
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.58,1:21:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快她會和另一個RahXephon降臨在這個世上
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.67,1:21:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個是假的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.09,1:21:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會加速世界的崩潰
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.34,1:21:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假的調率無法進行
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.09,1:22:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也明白這一點
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.68,1:22:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是無法阻止
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.27,1:22:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.18,1:22:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你就能辦到
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.35,1:22:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果是你就能辦到」
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.77,1:22:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.36,1:22:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是變成藍血的你和你的RahXephon的話
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.36,1:22:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止自己（久遠），進行新的世界的調率
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.70,1:22:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你，救救她
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.45,1:22:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你，為此你殺死我也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.04,1:22:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…因為我愛她
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.38,1:22:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我再次登上RahXephon，世界就能得救吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.55,1:22:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人君
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.30,1:22:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.30,1:22:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了你而去，是為了我自己而去
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.72,1:22:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了我想保護的人
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.56,1:22:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.98,1:22:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於成功了！
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.65,1:22:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是作戰部，也不是功刀那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.07,1:22:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.40,1:23:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色真大人
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.24,1:23:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令！
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.49,1:23:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事！
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.32,1:23:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紐約上空出現了MU的浮游都市
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.00,1:23:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫斯科上空也出現了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.58,1:23:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.00,1:23:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MU正在增殖
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.93,1:23:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，還以為再也見不到了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.10,1:23:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.85,1:23:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你，神名君
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.36,1:23:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你死
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.30,1:24:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.97,1:24:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.89,1:24:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要走啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.64,1:24:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須去做只有我才能辦到的事
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.64,1:24:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.14,1:24:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過再也不去駕駛RahXephon了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.06,1:24:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.48,1:24:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的血已經變藍了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.24,1:24:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次再坐上RahXephon，你就將不再是人類了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.66,1:24:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.24,1:24:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成藍血後，過去的記憶漸漸地就消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.33,1:24:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種各樣的記憶
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.33,1:24:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想失去…
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.59,1:24:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的回憶
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.26,1:24:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想忘記
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.17,1:24:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直到現在還喜歡著你
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.34,1:24:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.93,1:24:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我即將不再是我，不再是人類的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.27,1:24:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想忘記你的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.77,1:24:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，別過來
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.61,1:25:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能活下來
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.86,1:25:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變成什麼樣也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.19,1:25:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.29,1:25:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才相見，我一直在等待
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.04,1:25:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻…結果卻…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.88,1:25:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.55,1:25:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.05,1:25:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你等了這麼久，你還能這麼喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.39,1:25:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說太殘酷了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.72,1:25:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.48,1:25:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和我一起成長成大人吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.15,1:25:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己一個人變成了大人，對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.91,1:25:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.74,1:25:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.34,1:26:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.09,1:26:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.94,1:26:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入DEFCON-1狀態
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.53,1:26:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請根據緊急執行程序S-2進行行動
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.70,1:26:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複一遍
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.21,1:26:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「沒關係，因為願望已經實現」
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.04,1:26:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因為即使我已經變成了老太婆\N他還是接受了我」
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.30,1:26:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？你
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.38,1:26:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「只要有這份記憶在就可以活下去」
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.97,1:26:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，這裡是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.47,1:26:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「只要有這份記憶在，什麼事情都可以忍耐」
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.97,1:26:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.06,1:26:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「夢想不是成真了嗎？」
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.23,1:26:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.48,1:27:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，神名君會怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.48,1:27:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去記憶的神名君
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.40,1:27:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是沒有辦法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.07,1:27:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.07,1:27:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎樣的努力，也追不上神名君啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.99,1:27:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，為什麼沒有和他一起去
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.08,1:27:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為對像（目標）的存在，才能開始進行認識
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.59,1:27:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是這樣的，世界也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.42,1:27:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果失去了對象（目標），它自身也會消失
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.43,1:27:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在正處於這種沒有對象（目標）的狀態
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.93,1:27:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他追求，他痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.35,1:27:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他來到了這邊的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.69,1:27:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那比什麼都珍貴的心
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.86,1:27:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大半都被佔據了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.03,1:27:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被「你的事情」
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.36,1:27:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.53,1:27:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還來得及
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.45,1:27:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去你不是一直這樣做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.87,1:28:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直、一直地在追趕著神名君嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.87,1:28:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.63,1:28:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在等你
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.88,1:28:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊！我自己
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.14,1:28:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問題吧，她能到達嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.89,1:28:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的，因為她…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.35,1:29:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種歌聲，停止吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.10,1:29:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.69,1:29:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會輸，不可能輸的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.20,1:29:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為這個世界上的生物
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.78,1:29:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中部方面隊的來電
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.78,1:29:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未確認部隊在宮崎附近海面出現
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.45,1:29:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度170節
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.71,1:29:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在向中部方面飛行
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.29,1:29:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Terra本部的來電
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.54,1:29:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛行中的目標為5A
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.88,1:29:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認為RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.98,1:29:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.65,1:29:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.40,1:29:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天空迴響的歡欣的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.16,1:30:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你自身的音色
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.49,1:30:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此那是難以模仿的東西
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.33,1:30:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就在這裡…通向調律的門啊！打開吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.10,1:30:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.36,1:30:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.86,1:30:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是達到時間的彼岸的你的真實形態嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.54,1:30:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6點鐘方向，D-1！
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.62,1:30:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.46,1:30:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去瞭解痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.80,1:30:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽聽擁有記憶的、這個世界上生物的喊叫吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.30,1:31:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人！
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.64,1:31:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.22,1:31:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.89,1:31:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人！
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.99,1:31:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接受…我不會接受的
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.66,1:31:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都歸於無的世界！
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.74,1:31:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有浩子的世界！
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.25,1:31:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩子
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.18,1:31:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊，這也是一種人生啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.27,1:31:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想一直戰鬥到最後…
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.79,1:32:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon是眾多世界的流浪者
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.62,1:32:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使世界安定、調和的調律者
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.38,1:32:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的歌會使世界融為一體
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.38,1:32:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要恐懼，我的「另一半」啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.55,1:32:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的一切都是你的，你的一切都與我同在
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.39,1:32:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始是為了結束，而結束是為了開始
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.99,1:32:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐，請和綾人一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.08,1:32:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導他到不會再次消失的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.94,1:33:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊？伯父
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.61,1:33:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全島避難的命令已經發佈了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.44,1:33:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻無法和姐姐聯繫上
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.69,1:33:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙的話，由我和她聯繫
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.19,1:33:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠去做準備
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.53,1:33:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.70,1:33:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，不必慌張
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.29,1:33:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.46,1:33:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是遙吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.13,1:33:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.55,1:33:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人那個傢伙叫你了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.55,1:33:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我在RahXephon研究者中的是個無名之輩
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.22,1:33:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大體的情況還是想像的出來的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.23,1:34:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙，那是你選擇的道路吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.90,1:34:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.74,1:34:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.24,1:34:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在只能看著你…
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.75,1:34:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼，伯父
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.09,1:34:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.17,1:34:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.92,1:34:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.76,1:34:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑，盡全力地跑
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.93,1:34:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後，獲得幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.77,1:34:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.52,1:34:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.53,1:34:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.03,1:34:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是敵不過那個人啊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.03,1:34:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呀，還是想她獲得更像普通人的幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.70,1:35:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，好，我會很快讓你看到的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.64,1:35:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴貝姆先生
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.73,1:35:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.90,1:35:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儀式啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.48,1:35:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了迎接新的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.07,1:35:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把他殺了？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.99,1:35:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是殺了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.07,1:35:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是轉生了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.16,1:35:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像神名綾人一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.75,1:35:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此…
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.50,1:35:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等待這一天
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.25,1:35:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久以前，當這個身體還在MU的世界時
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.34,1:35:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我建造的RahXephon系統實驗失敗
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.35,1:35:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被炸飛到這個世界起，直到今天的此刻
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.85,1:36:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不知道更換了多少次
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.10,1:36:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底過了多少年，真是想都想不到啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.44,1:36:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.53,1:36:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是將世界向MU的方向調率嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.53,1:36:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的控制還沒有到這種程度
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.37,1:36:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.70,1:36:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是這樣接納他人而繼續生存下來的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.46,1:36:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接納他人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.63,1:36:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是按我自己的方式活下來而已
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.30,1:36:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了阻止因為世界的飽和而導致的宇宙的崩潰
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.05,1:36:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有製造出新的觀測者
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.14,1:36:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓那個觀測者看看我曾經所在的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.89,1:36:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是，我使之成功了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.15,1:36:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是事實上，世界正在面臨終結
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.73,1:36:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底這世界、這個宇宙會怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.07,1:36:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算讓那個少年做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.41,1:36:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經在時間的彼岸了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.58,1:37:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後他將選擇世界
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.33,1:37:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，除了MU的世界之外別無選擇
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.25,1:37:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說為什麼，這是因為他和我一樣流著MU的血液
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.17,1:37:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰也無法選擇自己的血
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.09,1:37:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.10,1:37:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果，我什麼也沒做
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.44,1:37:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導那個孩子的事情…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.53,1:37:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像個母親樣子的事情…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.70,1:37:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.40,1:38:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母大人
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.66,1:38:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.32,1:38:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你不在就好了…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.16,1:38:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.58,1:38:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不存在，那個孩子就不必如此痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.17,1:38:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你沒有讓他見到外面的世界…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.25,1:38:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！我只是…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.50,1:38:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛著那個孩子的只有我一個人就夠了…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.09,1:38:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.84,1:38:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使他痛苦是我的責任…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.43,1:38:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我創造了那個孩子…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.10,1:38:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我打算給予他一切…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.36,1:38:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該只有我才能支撐他的命運…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.03,1:39:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…那個孩子找到了自己的世界…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.03,1:39:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.45,1:39:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你在一起的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.29,1:39:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不能分擔他的痛苦了…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.88,1:39:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他不希望這樣…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.46,1:39:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不甘心
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.96,1:39:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他想要的是…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.55,1:39:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經消失了的遙遠往昔的回憶
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.97,1:39:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.64,1:39:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你那麼地想和他一起痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.48,1:39:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就讓你們一起痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.39,1:39:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只有你才能做得到…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.48,1:39:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.57,1:39:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的兒子就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.16,1:39:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母大人，我…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.18,1:40:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.60,1:40:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母大人
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.60,1:40:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.36,1:40:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了！
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.37,1:40:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有變
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.96,1:40:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份感覺和那時一點變化都沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.46,1:40:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.80,1:40:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去見他，見神名君
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.48,1:41:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君、神名君
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.15,1:41:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，你來了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.24,1:41:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.74,1:41:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是「現在」
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.66,1:41:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彙集與「過去」有關的故事的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.58,1:41:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是時間停止了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.75,1:41:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，我是活著…還是死了？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.26,1:41:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你活著啊
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.09,1:41:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.26,1:41:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也「存在」著
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.60,1:41:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時，無論何地
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.76,1:41:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我活在時間與時間的間隙裡
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.60,1:41:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為了時間的觀測者
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.61,1:41:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不是人類了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.94,1:41:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.03,1:41:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後會怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.19,1:41:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再次開始觀測時間，時間就會開始流逝
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.87,1:41:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去因為我不在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.45,1:41:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界充滿了不協調音
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.04,1:41:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.96,1:41:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不回去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.79,1:41:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.54,1:42:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界就會再度沾滿噪音
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.63,1:42:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能留在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.88,1:42:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾，因為我想你繼續活下去
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.55,1:42:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這個，我才選擇了留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.89,1:42:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你，神名君
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.65,1:42:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.90,1:42:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.99,1:42:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.99,1:42:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，最後讓你做次選擇
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.74,1:42:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是無法選擇未來
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.83,1:42:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為你是人類
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.16,1:42:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類之所以能作為人類生存下來
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.58,1:42:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為人類是做為過去記憶的彙集體而存在的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.84,1:42:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓你選擇的是過去
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.34,1:42:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得什麼樣的過去比較好
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.26,1:42:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我一直想和神名君呼吸同一個世界裡的空氣
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.94,1:43:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想和神名君踏著同一塊地面
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.61,1:43:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,度過相同的時間
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.86,1:43:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.44,1:43:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想和神名君一起變成大人
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.95,1:43:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.45,1:43:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.96,1:43:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡來並非只是你一個的願望
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.04,1:43:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是因為「過去的我」也這樣希望
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.55,1:43:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君也…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.39,1:43:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.55,1:43:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好像你也是的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.97,1:43:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時，因為神名君的心被你俘獲
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.73,1:43:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以神名君與你相遇
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.90,1:43:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也與神名君邂逅
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.73,1:43:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於我們而言
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.24,1:43:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.57,1:43:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你沒有來，如果你沒有這樣期望
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.49,1:43:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界就會回歸到無
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.49,1:44:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，即使是我們也無法逆轉時間
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.00,1:44:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做為補償，送給你們「回憶」
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.67,1:44:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該真正度過的兩個人的「一生的時間」
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.77,1:44:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.19,1:44:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們的…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.44,1:44:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.36,1:44:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就從這裡開始的
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.36,1:44:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人的回憶…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.04,1:44:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們今後打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.21,1:44:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是RahXephon吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.54,1:44:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是返回我們應該去的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.96,1:44:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們不會感到孤獨的
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.63,1:44:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為，我們兩個在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.89,1:44:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，請過的幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.89,1:45:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是應該由我們對你們說的
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.73,1:45:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.44,1:45:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？發生了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.19,1:45:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這是我製造出來的系統的光芒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.45,1:45:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.28,1:45:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.03,1:46:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們，不，是我們的繼承者們的選擇
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.79,1:46:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說他背叛了嗎？奏者他
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.38,1:46:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛？你再說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.46,1:46:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他繼承了MU和人類的血
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.05,1:46:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們所有人的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.14,1:46:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個少年的血是藍的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.64,1:46:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我是同一種血
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.22,1:46:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍血又能代表什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.56,1:46:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是想拯救這個由你發端
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.89,1:46:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我們造成的現在的這種窘境啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.40,1:46:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為想要活下去的人的責任
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.15,1:46:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.57,1:46:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？巴貝姆先生
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.91,1:46:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不應該承擔起責任嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.74,1:46:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是創世主啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.66,1:46:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人可以接近的神，根本不是神！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.34,1:46:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，多虧了麻彌
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.67,1:47:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，是這樣嗎，姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.68,1:47:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，回去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.18,1:47:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去？去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.18,1:47:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想念的人的身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.94,1:47:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始是為了結束，而結束是為了開始
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.74,1:48:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨在不可思議的國度
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.15,1:48:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直做著長夢
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.16,1:48:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到短暫的夏日終結
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.33,1:48:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色的晚霞中
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.58,1:48:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都是搖蕩的預感
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.67,1:48:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的世界不是夢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.26,1:48:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，奶奶
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.09,1:48:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果愛麗斯真的回到了現實世界嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.43,1:48:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼問？
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.43,1:48:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說「人的世界不是夢境」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.44,1:48:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是愛麗斯真的去過夢中的世界嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.86,1:48:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就結果而言，愛麗斯回到了現實世界
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.70,1:48:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實那根本無關緊要
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.87,1:48:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這與哪邊的世界是現實世界沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.87,1:48:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為，她留下了記憶
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.04,1:48:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鏡中國度裡體驗的絕妙回憶
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.13,1:49:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少對她而言是現實吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.88,1:49:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就夠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.97,1:49:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.81,1:49:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶真的很喜歡爺爺呢
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.39,1:49:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.39,1:49:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為奶奶每說幾句話就會提起爺爺
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.48,1:49:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.65,1:49:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣啊，爺爺真的是被愛著啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.07,1:49:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺也很愛奶奶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.16,1:49:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要捉弄大人
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.58,1:49:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於愛的事情就說到這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.83,1:49:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的太多喉嚨都干了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.00,1:49:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我去取茶
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.34,1:49:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有麥茶
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.09,1:49:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑，危險，玲香
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.42,1:49:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.94,1:50:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.37,1:50:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶，久等了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.20,1:50:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.70,1:50:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.04,1:50:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.54,1:50:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又跑到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.29,1:50:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.63,1:50:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡啊？


